com.misc.common.moplaf.dbsynch

Interface DataSource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DbSynchUnitAbstract, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataSourceJdbc
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataSourceImpl, DataSourceJdbcImpl

    public interface DataSource
extends DbSynchUnitAbstract
    A representation of the model object 'Data Source'.

    A DataSource is the top level DbSynchUnit in the hierarchy of the synch units.

    Next to its functionality as synch unit, the DataSource supports the connection with the database.

    Specialization of this class implements the up and down synchronization of a given Table:

    • synchUpTableImpl(Table)
    • synchDownTableImpl(Table)

    The following features are supported:

    • Connected
    See Also:
    DbSynchPackage.getDataSource()
